        <sponsor name-id="T000468">Ms. Titus</sponsor> (for
			 herself, <cosponsor name-id="L000397">Ms. Lofgren</cosponsor>,
			 <cosponsor name-id="S001185">Ms. Sewell of Alabama</cosponsor>, and
			 <cosponsor name-id="F000455">Ms. Fudge</cosponsor>) introduced the following
			 bill; which was referred to the <committee-name committee-id="HED00">Committee
			 on Education and the Workforce</committee-name>
